def: The act of disjoining, or state of being disjoined; separation.Fuller.
A genus of water fowls, of the order Anseres, including certainspecies of fresh-water ducks.
A man who is engaged in quarrying stones; a quarrier.
A frame of adjustable boards erected on a post, and havingholes through which the head and hands of an offender were thrust soas to be exposed in front of it. Shak.
To deliver from the form or nature of a beast.
An Asiatic name for Melia Azadirachta, and M. Azedarach. SeeMargosa.
The name of several cruciferous plants of the genus Brassica(formerly Sinapis), as white mustard (B. alba), black mustard (B.Nigra), wild mustard or charlock (B. Sinapistrum).
A proud or haughty person. Sylvester.
